product_name: Estee LauderFuturist Soft Touch Brightening Skincealer Concealer
summary: SummaryHighlightsSustainable PackagingEstée Lauder Futurist Soft Touch Brightening Skincealer Concealer is an innovative "skincealer" that combines the performance of a long-wearing brightening concealer with the efficacy of skincare.
details: DetailsBenefitsLook brighter now. Even brighter in the future.With this innovative Skincealer formula, skin is instantly hydrated and looks brighter, more radiant, more perfected. Plumps fine, dry lines and improves hydration and radiance over time.The exclusive soft-touch applicator is based on the shape of a fingertip. Designed for precision application and easy blending in all areas.Delivers the performance of a long-wearing, medium-to-full coverage brightening concealer - plus the efficacy of skincare.After 1 week: Hydration and radiance are measurably increased.After 4 weeks: Fine lines and dark circles look reduced. Undereye firmness is improved.With continued use: The telltale undereye area looks smoother, more radiant. Crepiness appears reduced.Key IngredientsVitamin C Brightening Complex: Helps diminish the look of undereye circles and bring new radiance to the undereye area.Tri-Firming Complex: Helps skin feel firmer, look more resilient. Helps reduce the look of lines.Hyaluronic Acid Complex: Dual molecular weight Hyaluronic Acid helps retain moisture on the surface of the skin and provides hydration. Plus, an algae extract helps plump skin with hydration.Silky hybrid formula covers and brightens dark circles. Soft Radiant finish. Water-, sweat- and humidity-resistant. All-day color true wear. Non-creasing, non-poring.Formulated WithoutParabensPhthalatesSulfitesSulfatesParaffinPetrolatumDrying AlcoholSynthetic ColorsItem 2618165How To UseChoose a concealer shade that matches your skintone and foundation or is one shade lighter.Find your perfect shade: Choose your skin's intensity level (from ultra light to very deep) and undertone (cool, neutral or warm).HOW TO DETERMINE YOUR UNDERTONE: Undertone is the way your bare skin looks and behaves. Which one sounds most like you?Cool (C) undertones: Bare skin has a rosy tone and burns easily in the sun.Neutral (N) undertones: Bare skin is more even toned, not too pink or golden.Warm (W) undertones: Bare skin has a golden or olive tone and tans easily in the sun.Apply this brightening concealer as needed to cover-up dark circles, spots, imperfections, more.IngredientsDimethicone, Water\Aqua\Eau, Methyl Trimethicone, Butylene Glycol, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Phenyl Trimethicone, Neopentyl Glycol Diheptanoate, Glycerin, Peg-10 Dimethicone, Trametes Versicolor Extract, PEG/PPG-18/18 Dimethicone, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Dimethicone/PEG-10/15 Crosspolymer, Sodium Hyaluronate, Acetyl Hexapeptide-8, Algae Extract, Cholesterol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Extract, Tocopheryl Acetate, Squalane, Hordeum Vulgare Extract\Extrait D'Orge, Laminaria Digitata Extract, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract, Hydrolyzed Yeast Protein, Hydrolyzed Rice Extract, Narcissus Tazetta Bulb Extract, BHT, Tocopherol, Lecithin, Triethoxycaprylylsilane, Disodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Aluminum Dimyristate, Lauryl Peg-9 Polydimethylsiloxyethyl Dimethicone, Propylene Carbonate, Sodium Chloride, Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Citrate, Caprylyl Glycol, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Disodium Edta, Dipropylene Glycol, Chlorphenesin, Phenoxyethanol, Laureth-7. reviews.headline: Not worth the money
reviews.comments: Used it a couple times, immediately settled in my fine lines. I took it back.

reviews.headline: one of the best concealers
reviews.comments: repeat purchase, after trying so many concealers. this has just the right texture, pigment, and coverage that works on dark circles. loved that Ulta had my shade already remembered, as we sometimes forget what shade we have used.

reviews.headline: Smooth natural coverage
reviews.comments: I am always looking for the perfect concealer for under eye use. One of my friends recommended this concealer so I decided to try it. This product provides nice smooth natural coverage. Not too heavy and not too light. The applicator sponge tip has a different shape but is easy to use. The product is creamy and not sticky and leaves a nice natural look without making your skin look dried out. Lots of good color choices to choose from. The Ulta makeup artist decided I have a cool undertone so I'm trying the color she recommended.  So far I do like the product and am pleased with it.

reviews.headline: Skincealer
reviews.comments: This concealer looks good and matches my skin tone well once rubbed in.  It does have a brightening effect that makes me look more awake and vibrant (I am perennially tired).  It's a bit thicker than I would like, but it didn't sit in my fine lines.  A little bit is all it takes for good coverage.  I used it with my EL Double Wear foundation and cream eyeshadow.  No separation was noted.

reviews.headline: I really love it
reviews.comments: I really love the weightless feel, it blends into my skin effortlessly with just my fingertip. I'm not the most knowledgeable nor skilled person when it comes to makeup. Therefore anything that's simple & doesn't make me break out or clog my pores i'm happy with. I have A LOT of medical skin issues so I rather just wear glasses, sunblock & use prescription skin care & otc skin care products. What i absolutely love about this concealer is that i can just use it to spot cover & matches my skin tone so well that even though blemishes might still be a little visible, I like it because you can't tell theres any on. But when i use for undereyes, usually on days i actually have somewhere to be seen, I add a foundation as well. It's very blendable, but it does crease. However, it could entirely be my fault because i do not know what I should buy or can even tell you what type of skin I have (i.e dry, oily, combination etc.). Still i recommend you buy this!

reviews.headline: Creases
reviews.comments: It creases and cracks. For the price it shouldn't do either.

reviews.headline: Will buy again
reviews.comments: Covers my dark spots

reviews.headline: My Favorite Concealer
reviews.comments: Love how  many different shades this product comes in so I can switch at different times of year.

reviews.headline: Don't like
reviews.comments: I cant get this to work for me. It breaks up and creases extremely bad. Wish I could still return it.

reviews.headline: Best paired with Futurist Concealer
reviews.comments: Very full coverage, but when paired with matching shade in futurist line, it looks PERFECT. Didn't even need to set it, absolutely no creasing.

reviews.headline: Love this stuff!
reviews.comments: Covers great & doesnt feel heavy

reviews.headline: Perfect for older skin
reviews.comments: I don't wear foundation and I use this to touch up the problem areas and throw some finishing powder on and I'm set for the day. This is the best concealer for older skin. I am 56 and this does not settle in my fine lines. Highly recommend!!!

reviews.headline: BEST CONCEALER
reviews.comments: i have sensitive acne prone skin combo skin and have been LOYAL to mac prolongwear ever since highschool (24 now) and this FAR exceeded my expectations. the formula is light in texture and feel, but super high coverage. when i look at my face with just this on and a KISS of powder it looks good in the CAR MIRROR. it's an investment due to the price, but for how long it wears and how beautiful it looks on the skin it's definitely worth it.

reviews.headline: Love this product
reviews.comments: So light and easy to blend

reviews.headline: Best concealer
reviews.comments: Just the right consistency

reviews.headline: Lovely!
reviews.comments: I use this for my dark under eyes, acne, and redness around the nose. Covers them up like a charm. It says brightening but if you get a shade that matches your skin tone rather than going with a lighter shade for highlighting you can use it on other areas other than dark circles.

reviews.headline: Perfect Brightening Concealer
reviews.comments: This concealer is great for maturing skin by providing a brightening glow. It is not too heavy like the double wear concealer.

reviews.headline: Does not conceal
reviews.comments: I bought, and liked, the primer and foundation of this line so i figured i would try the comcealer. It might be ok if you have zero skin concerns, but it didnt cover my dark circles or blemishes, also creased and settled into fine lines. The shades are also comparatively much lighter than the corresponding foundation shades. I purchased the Futurist foundation in 1n2, Ecru. In the concealer i got 1C, and its at least a shade too light.

reviews.headline: This does just what it says.
reviews.comments: I like this product. The coverage is medium, but has a natural look.

reviews.headline: Pleased with product
reviews.comments: Worked very well.

faceoff_positive.comments:
I am in love with this concealer. I have it in the shade 1N. This incredible formula completely covers & brightens dark circles/gives skin instant moisture, leaving it feeling & looking more hydrated, radiant, and resilient/plumps, tightens, firms & smooths the under-eye giving you a more "glow from within" & more youthful look/reduces the appearance of fine lines & wrinkles over time/blends easily, effortlessly & seemlessly with your actual fingertips or even better with the unique soft fingertip/dries to a beautiful radiant flawless finish and doesn't budget for water, humidity, or even sweat/is never poring, doesn't crease or get cakey/come in a wide variety of shades to match any skin tone and under tone as well as options lighter and darker that you can purchase for contour and highlighting like I do. The ingredients in this formula make this an all in 1 makeup and skincare product as they not only help you achieve a beautiful and flawless makeup application but offers instant skin benefits as well as improved skin over all after continuous use. I am completely blown away by this new formula and again, she is going to be my new holy-grail, can't live without, must have product! I have already ordered a few of these since receiving this one! 

*I received this product complimentary from Estee Lauder & Influenster in exchange for my honest review. Opinions are always my own*
faceoff_positive.headline: My New Favorite, HOLY-GRAIL, Must Have, Concealer!

faceoff_negative.comments: Let me start by saying my skin has dry patches and lacking moisture due to winter which changes the way this concealer works in my opinion. The packaging is gorgeous. Heavy, easy to use. I love the wand applicator. Doesn't pull out tons of product like other brands. The product is thick, easy to apply, but does take work to blend given its thickness. It brightens just like it says and makes my eye area radiant. I'm acne prone and I've used this over my cheeks and forehead with no breakouts. As for sweat-proof it does roll off the makeup, but I crease badly where I accumulate oil. It also clings to any dry patch I have on my face making it look like I applied powder over it. That's another star. I think this product would be best for combo to oily skin and simply not for us dry girls. Overall the product is great, just not for my skin type.
faceoff_negative.headline: Didn't work for me
